            </p>
            <p>
              With Govrn, this second step is issued via SMS, giving organizations a fast, reliable, and secure method to confirm user identity before granting access to sensitive governance data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why SMS-Based MFA Matters -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
